. 50, no. 70 (Sept. 3, 1972).", "\"Serving the Chapel Hill area since 1923.\"", "Also issued on microfilm.", "Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection.", "Chapel Hill newspaper (DLC)sn 92073233 (OCoLC)9747649"], "number": ["sn92073229", "00332891868", "1"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn92073229"], "number_reel": ["00332891868"], "numeric_shelf_id": 195803201, "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_formats": [{"label": "MODSXML Record", "link": "//tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//ncu/batch_ncu_dowe_ver01/data/sn92073229/00332891868/1958032001/1958032001_1.xml"}, {"label": "MARCXML Record", "link": "//lccn.loc.gov/sn92073229/marcxml"}], "partof": [{"count": 2534, "title": "the chapel hill weekly (chapel hill, n.c.) 1923-1972", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:the+chapel+hill+weekly+%28chapel+hill,+n.c.%29+1923-1972&fo=json"}, {"count": 3203926, "title": "chronicling america", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/chronicling-america/?fo=json"}, {"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["the chapel hill weekly (chapel hill, n.c.) 1923-1972"], "place_of_publication": "Chapel Hill, N.C.", "publication_frequency": ["semiweekly"], "raw_lccn": "sn 92073229 ", "reel_numbers": ["00332891868"], "resources": [{"files": 12, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_dowe_ver01:data:sn92073229:00332891868:1958032001:0219/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn92073229/1958-03-20/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn92073229, 1958-03-20, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ncu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["chapel hill", "orange county", "chapel hill (n.c.)", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange"], "subject_headings": ["Chapel Hill (N.C.)--Newspapers", "Orange County (N.C.)--Newspapers", "North Carolina--Chapel Hill", "North Carolina--Orange County", "United States--North Carolina--Orange--Chapel Hill"], "subjects": [{"chapel hill": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:chapel+hill&fo=json"}, {"chapel hill (n.c.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:chapel+hill+%28n.c.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"north carolina": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:north+carolina&fo=json"}, {"orange": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:orange&fo=json"}, {"orange county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:orange+county&fo=json"}, {"orange county (n.c.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:orange+county+%28n.c.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-08-13T01:15:05.575Z", "title": "The Chapel Hill weekly (Chapel Hill, N.C.), March 20, 1958", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/1958-03-20/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn92073229", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/d42fd920-47cb-5ef9-be84-79e76cdcf357"], "batch": ["ncu_curry_ver02"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1923", "description": ["Semiweekly, May 10, 1955-Sept. 3, 1972 Vol. 1, no. 1 (Mar. 1, 1923)-v. 50, no. 70 (Sept. 3, 1972). \"Serving the Chapel Hill area since 1923.\" Also issued on microfilm. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Chapel Hill newspaper (DLC)sn 92073233 (OCoLC)9747649"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:05.831Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-03", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-03"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [35.910262, -79.055474], "location": ["chapel hill", "orange county", "united states", "north carolina", "orange"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-79.055474, 35.910262], "number": ["2533", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "microfilm master", "27098353", "2025-07-01t13:41:10.400000", "sn92073229", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/1963-12-29/ed-1/", "north carolina div of archives & hist", "east carolina univ", "2023-08-09t16:16:15.715047", "2766-6050", "online resource", "chapel hill pub libr", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/1923-03-01/ed-1/", "sn92073233", "microfilm service copy"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the chapel hill weekly (chapel hill, n.c.) 1923-1972", "serial and government publications division", "catalog"], "publication_frequency": ["semiweekly"], "score": 78.96724, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["chapel hill", "orange county", "chapel hill (n.c.)", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:33:58.694Z", "title": "The Chapel Hill weekly", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn92073229/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270622/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1923", "dates": ["[1923 TO 1972]"], "description": ["Semiweekly, May 10, 1955-Sept. 3, 1972 Began with vol. I, no. 1 (March 1, 1923); ceased v. 50, no. 70 (Sept. 3, 1972). \"Serving the Chapel Hill area since 1923.\" Also issued on microfilm. Vol. I, No. 1 (March 1, 1923); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 19, 2021). Volume 41, Number 103 (December 29, 1963) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 19, 2021). Chapel Hill newspaper"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:58.293Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270622/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["chapel hill", "orange county", "united states", "north carolina", "orange"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2766-6069", "1231983097", "2021270622", "online resource"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the chapel hill weekly (chapel hill, n. c.) 1923-1972 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["semiweekly"], "score": 69.75985, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["chapel hill", "orange county", "chapel hill (n.c.)", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:02:54.346Z", "title": "The Chapel Hill weekly", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021270622/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271240/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1879", "dates": ["[1879 TO 1999]"], "description": ["Weekly, Oct. 13, 1911- Began in 1879. Published as: Recorder and North Carolina tobacco journal, <Apr. 18, 1883->. Published as: Hillsboro recorder, Nov. 14, 1895 and Dec. 12, 1895. Published in Hillsboro, N.C., Aug. 7, 1895-<Dec. 19, 1895>. Publisher: The Durham Sun Publishing Company, <January 5-December 29, 1911>. Democratic. Issues for <July 2, 1879-Nov. 29, 1882> also called: Old ser., no. 59-63. Issues for <Apr. 18, 1883-Dec. 29, 1911> have vol. numbering as: Vol. 63, no. 29-v. 92, no. 35. Description based on: New Series----Vol. 1, No. 2 (July 2, 1879); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 23, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Volume 92, Number 35 (December 29, 1911) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 23, 2016)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:37.472Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271240/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["orange county", "hillsboro", "durham", "united states", "hillsborough", "durham county", "north carolina", "orange"], "number": ["964078563", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2016271238", "2475-0891", "2016271239", "online resource", "2016271240"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Recorder and North Carolina tobacco journal", "Hillsboro recorder"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the durham recorder (durham, n. c.) 1879-19?? [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.173946, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["durham county (n.c.)", "orange county", "hillsboro", "durham", "durham county", "hillsborough", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange", "hillsborough (n.c.)", "durham (n.c.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:54:14.600Z", "title": "The Durham recorder", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2016271240/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271244/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1887", "dates": ["[1887 TO 1899]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with vol. I, No. 1 (August 11, 1887). Description based on: Vol. I, No. 1 (August 11, 1887); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Vol. I, No. 52 (August 2, 1888) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:37.472Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271244/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["orange county", "hillsboro", "united states", "hillsborough", "north carolina", "orange"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "964614496", "2016271244", "online resource", "2475-157x", "2016271240"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "hillsboro recorder (hillsboro, n.c.) 1887-18?? [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.173946, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["orange county", "hillsboro", "hillsborough", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange", "hillsborough (n.c.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:54:14.600Z", "title": "Hillsboro recorder", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2016271244/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271245/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1820", "dates": ["[1820 TO 1879]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1820; ceased in 1879. Democratic. Issues for <Jan. 26, 1870-Mar. 5, 1879> have vol. numbering: New ser., v. 2, no. 1-v.7, no. 8 = old ser., v. 50-59. Suspended Apr. 19-May 3, May 17-June 26, 1865. Available on microfilm from North Carolina Dept. of Archives and History. Description based on: Vol. XVI, No. 805 (February 5, 1836); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016). Latest issue consulted: New Series----Vol. 7. No. 3---- (January 22, 1879) ----Old Series, Vol. 58. (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016). Durham recorder 2475-0891 (DLC) 2016271240 (OCoLC)964078563"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:37.472Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271245/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["orange county", "hillsboro", "united states", "hillsborough", "north carolina", "orange"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2475-1618", "online resource", "964624444", "2016271240", "2016271245"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the hillsborough recorder (hillsborough, n. c.) 1820-1879 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.173946, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["orange county", "hillsboro", "hillsborough", "united states", "orange county (n.c.)", "north carolina", "newspapers", "orange", "hillsborough (n.c.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:54:14.600Z", "title": "The Hillsborough recorder", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2016271245/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271246/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1880", "dates": ["[1880 TO 1918]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1880. Ceased in 1918? New ser. v. 8, no. 48 skipped in enumeration; n.s. v. 10, no. 51-52 skipped in enumeration. Two issues called n.s. v. 9, no. 28, Apr. 12, 1890 and Apr. 19, 1890. New ser. v. 10, no. 24, Apr. 4, 1891, misdated as Mar. 4, 1891 in masthead; n.s. v. 15, no. 2 Dec. 7, 1895, misdated as Nov. 7, 1895 in masthead. Some issues have \"Supplement\". Democratic. Description based on: New Series.-Vol. I.-No. 3. (October 23, 1880); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016). Latest issue consulted: New Series Vol. XXVIII, No 17 (May 11, 1916) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 30, 2016)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:37.472Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271246/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "location": ["orange county", "united states", "hillsborough", "north carolina", "orange"], "number": ["2016271246", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "964628528", "online resource", "2475-1669"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "orange county observer (hillsborough, n. c.;hillsborough, n.c.;hillsboro, n.c.) 1880-1918 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 44.173946, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject